snippet.title: Mega Man SFR - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Mega Man: Super Fighting Robot is finally out! Enjoy!

Download: https://mega.nz/#!FtRQASgA!BElAWMj2ALYvWgJmhEbcwVxm4Bcb3pic5eyyAw2ozuU
Newest version: 1.0.5 (October 8, 2015)

Visit the official Mega Man: SFR Facebook page!
https://www.facebook.com/Mega-Man-Super-Fighting-Robot-402614193259545

Also, you can download the OST here. Several composers came together to give this game some awesome music.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jOcOH3HfN80
